，都係我錯。今次脫離群眾路線，深刻反省，引咎辭職。唔好殺我，我唔想成鄭曉鬆同志，唔想抑鬱症跳樓自殺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「國務院港澳事務辦公室官網釋出訊息：中央人民政府駐澳門特別行政區聯絡辦公室主任鄭曉鬆同志因患抑鬱症於2018年10月20日晚在其澳門住所墜樓身亡。」"},{"pid":"5d745467ab368f6d949a7cabe1779a8284b4c871","tid":1756250,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:32:25.000Z","msg":"之後咪滲透中間既民主派，希望挖角分裂。"},{"pid":"7a40e6563155d51d920eccdb00c6da81a297db55","tid":1756250,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:33:06.000Z","msg":"Google map個山莊似係起深圳市中心西北面<br />\n魔法射程唔夠遠"},{"pid":"2dbe00ed96c12da428bd590966258d751b8a87c1","tid":1756250,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:41:57.000Z","msg":"一國兩制  港人治港  高度自治<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e57408d7474864564e0adb347ed029e9a7c11c2","tid":1756250,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:43:15.000Z","msg":"一國兩制<br />\n中英聯合聲明"},{"pid":"c225e6e31dc39c57856b1d9341d7e192dcf87fba","tid":1756250,"uid":120955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:57:01.000Z","msg":"太陽照常升起？"}]}